{"id": "1203393900023123988", "channel_id": "1203393900023123988", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為普5，已經用掉\n剩下：\n紅夫人（0啟過不去，我商店提升到1啟）、\n希洛、\n帶了一隻朵爾（補血用）\n莉莉（自己的0啟）\n\n因為沒有艾繼絲，\n銀曜：腦中、刻印（易傷）是關鍵\n\n道中：大部分依靠紅夫人狂氣爆發收一波\n\n刻印：力量、狂氣、易傷，這三個很重要\n\n至於，鏡像有的話，給報償打擊\n\n\n莉莉的報償，要稍微看一下\n盡量保留在精英/Boss\n\n朵爾：狂氣回充為主\n希洛：工具人，\n耐力集滿、Boss中易傷\n報償打擊，傷害很可觀\n\n\n至於身上的命輪，我亂搭的，看看就行了\n\n然後一樣，除了朵爾外\n我全部穿埋骨地，疊死抗", "timestamp": "2024-02-03T17:37:43.743000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1203393900296015912", "filename": "1706980994828.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 122999, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1203393900023123988/1203393900296015912/1706980994828.jpg?ex=69cc0667&is=69cab4e7&hm=12f6c582ffb2c2ce0ce890f10c02e227dbe1047586b66444eb3ad2b2eac17df2&"}, {"id": "1203393900581097472", "filename": "1706980994819.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 133605, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1203393900023123988/1203393900581097472/1706980994819.jpg?ex=69cc0667&is=69cab4e7&hm=2ec2ed4a162af08d207bdb6a1834c9d4f5d018210490a1f0617dd7c641d14ce4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203393900023123988", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉：莉莉之融災（普4）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
